::Dollen::

       Dollen saw GoldenEye hit.  OH NO!!!!  He looked at KitKat.

              "Don't worry commander, I'll get her to a CR right away," He
said and carried GoldenEye off to a CR.  He watched her in there, and hoped
that she would get better.

                 "I love you," He said, and ran back out to the battlefield.
He fired 2 missiles at Deemos.
